German Investors Slam Czech Business Environment, Lidovky Says

-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 
2011-04-07T06:26:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/german-investors-slam-czech-business-environment-lidovky-says.html
German companies operating in the
 Czech Republic  are not satisfied with business conditions in the
country,  Lidove Noviny  reported, citing a survey by the Czech-
German Chamber of Commerce and Industry.  One third of German businesses in the Czech Republic say
they would now choose a different country if they were to decide
on an investment location again, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Laca in Prague at 
 placa@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Willy Morris at 
 wmorris@bloomberg.net  